Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In 1912, fragments from a\Ngravel pit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:08.65,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,in Sussex seemed to give\NBritish science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:11.47,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,the fossil it wanted, a\Nhuman-like skull,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,an ape-like jaw, a famous\Nname, Piltdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:17.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.64,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The evidence was thin, but\Nthe story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.08,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,was powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.17,0:00:24.38,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It fit a brain-first\Ntheory and gave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.59,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Britain its own ancient\Nancestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Some anatomists doubted\Nthe skull and jaw
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:32.25,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,belonged together, but\Naccess was limited, prestige
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.66,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,was heavy, and the\Nspecimen kept circulating
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:37.07,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,as authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.03,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The fraud was not perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:40.44,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:45.32,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,By 1953, Tess exposed the\Ntrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.19,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The skull was a recent\Nhuman bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:49.54,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The jaw was from an\Norangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.50,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The teeth had been filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.39,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The bones had been\Nstained.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The hoax survived because\Nit let the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.36,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,field feel correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The mystery fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:01.32,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The receipts remain.
